The rescue of the woman, who had not been identified, was captured in dramatic footage by ABC 15 in Phoenix.

In the video, a man is seen signaling to a a Maricopa County Sheriff's Office chopper surveying the area. He appears to be indicating to them that someone needs help at a nearby van.

Two deputies walk over to them van as deadly rushing waters cover them to their waist.

It looks like the van will be underwater in minutes.

